  "time_ut": 1658313456,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u2018\u2018\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dba \u0d85\u0db1\u0db4\u0dda\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dd2\u0dad \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dd2\u0db5\u0dbd\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbd\u0dd9\u0dc3 \u0db8\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dda \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dc4\u0dd0\u2018\u2018",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"I do not consider this to be an unexpected result.\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In this parliament, a political camp has been created that is opposite to us. Mr. Anura Dissanayake, presidential election candidate of the National People's Force, said in the parliament that there is a need for ideological activity with that camp.",
        "Mr. Anura Kumara Dissanayake said that there has been a big contradiction between the people outside and the Parliament.",
        "The Sahab leader of the candidates proposes the Treasurer of Pohottuwa. It is usually called the President's Party. Because G. We saw that through the confirmation of Mr. L. Peiris. Also, Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe's school friend Dinesh Gunawardena, who comes from an old left-wing historical family, proposed the leader of the United National Party.",
        "It's just like the secretary's team in the bud. But we also know that the secretary is haunted by some ghost. That is politics.",
        "Therefore, even if there was a vote between those two camps, I contested by focusing on our unique politics and our policy. I do not consider this to be an unexpected result that is at all surprising. This is the nature of the composition that is being shown in the Parliament of our country today. But I also believe that the actual composition of the earth today is not the composition shown in the figures in this parliament. Therefore, if anyone today believes that a reflection of the fair will of the people appeared in this parliament, it is a complete illusion. This shows a distorted reflection of the will of the people. Remember that. A great contradiction has been created among you people in this chamber. A great contradiction has been created between the people outside and this council. But nothing more than this is expected from this parliament."
      ],
